MMSegmentation 1.1.0 installation:

pip install -U openmim
mim install mmengine
mim install "mmcv==2.0.1"

pip install "mmsegmentation==1.0.0"

pip install reedmuller

Link dataset:
mkdir -p data
ln -s /beegfs/data/shared/cityscapes_daformer data/cityscapes


Training:
sbatch tools/slurm_train.sh configs/segformer_mit-b0_8xb1-160k_cityscapes-1024x1024.py --work-dir <work_dir path>

Testing:
sbatch tools/slurm_test.sh configs/segformer_mit-b0_8xb1-160k_cityscapes-1024x1024.py <path to pth checkpoint file>
